{
  "stem": "15393.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When this happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[CRYING] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother asked the doctors would they look at her, and there was no-- there was no hope at all.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was none.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my mother then managed to escape from the ghetto, from the burning ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She had just went out completely in her eyes, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Took the arm band off, and walked through town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And nobody stopped her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she came to me, or rather, to ask where we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[CRYING] And from May '43, we were together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from May '43 until now, we are together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she-- we were four people by that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This poor Frau Wieth had four of us then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [DRINKS] And we were sleeping on the floor in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Every night.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one morning very early, about six o'clock in the morning-- our sleep was not a very deep sleep.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were incredibly alert to every sound, to every slightest, slightest motion anywhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the kitchen was very near the entrance door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We sat and we heard definitely like somebody is by the door, like walking the steps and by the door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was no need to walk the steps, because there was a lift.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But there was somebody definitely walking the steps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was by the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Instantly, we cleared up ourselves off into the scullery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There was a scullery the size of-- I don't know, I mean-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] six feet by six.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I mean, tiny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Just to put a few things in-- in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "All of us into that scullery, and no sign of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
